  <refnamediv>
    <refname>krig_doe_crit_3</refname>
    <refpurpose>a function dedicated to design of experiment</refpurpose>
  </refnamediv>
  
  <refsynopsisdiv>
    <title>Calling Sequence</title>
    <synopsis>Res = krig_doe_crit_3(Model,x,fmin)</synopsis>
  </refsynopsisdiv>
  
  <refsection>
    <title>Parameters</title>
    <variablelist>
      <varlistentry>
        <term>Model</term>
        <listitem>
          <para>the kriging structure of the model to be learnt online.</para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>
      <varlistentry>
        <term>x</term>
        <listitem>
          <para>a proposal point to be added in the learning data set.</para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>
      <varlistentry>
        <term>fmin</term>
        <listitem>
          <para>the minimum value of the data set.</para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>
      <varlistentry>
        <term>Res</term>
        <listitem>
          <para>the objective function value.</para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>
    </variablelist>
  </refsection>
  
  <refsection>
    <title>Description</title>
    <para>The point that maximize this function is a good candidate point to improve the kriging model.
      This function computes y_var.</para>
  </refsection>
  
